---
import lismyhero from '../images/lismy-hero.jpg'
---
<section class="hero w-full flex flex-col  h-[667px] items-center justify-end md:-mt-20 ">
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:mb-28 lg:mx-[20%] space-y-2 flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-slate-500 p-6 text-center bg-opacity-50 lg:rounded-2xl ">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">¡Dale Vida a Tus Manos!</h1>
        <p class="text-white font-semibold text-2xl" >Descubre una experiencia de manicure excepcional que transformará tus uñas en verdaderas obras de arte. ¡Haz que tus manos y pies brillen con Elegancia y Glamour!</p>
        <button class="text-white text-2xl border-2 border-white font-bold bg-pink-500 py-4 px-8  rounded-2xl hover:scale-105 hover:bg-white hover:text-pink-500 hover:border-pink-500 transition-all">BOOK NOW</button>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .hero {
        background-image: url("../images/lismy-hero.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: top center;
    }
</style>

